{"tid":1426022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"881:鐳射筆 強光係武器 咁警方攻擊示威者 記者又點計","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:09:14.000Z","uid":2036,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0280caf9d73f1513acbe7651f852b48c659cc81a","tid":1426022,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:16:32.000Z","msg":"呢個point 唔錯<br />\n<br />\n記者會可以諗點煲<br />\n<br />\n鴨寮街仲唔做軍火庫？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n881:鐳射筆 強光係武器 咁警方攻擊示威者 記者又點計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐳射筆 鐳射槍 觀星筆點分<br />\n鐳射筆係攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n以前有無用鐳射筆攻擊人紀錄？<br />\n<br />\n鐳射槍照射警員不適有幾多數據 <br />\n幾多人傷 傷勢如何<br />\n<br />\n警方用強光 鐳射照示威者 記者<br />\n是否正在使用武力既一種<br />\n<br />\n無 咁就雙重標準<br />\n有 ？咁有無使用指引"},{"pid":"b558503daac7f0c0f79a5f98d26f369911dcbdae","tid":1426022,"uid":222190,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeoUZHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeoUZHP.png&h=b44c7291&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081935_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081935_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=df557be6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081937_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081937_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=8fb455f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081939_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081939_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png&h=38f4eb48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081943_85a1606fcfc9b08c9dc289c763a99128.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081943_85a1606fcfc9b08c9dc289c763a99128.png&h=adc8245b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081947_93c62c32dc6d38ba7f06ff3a9596eb9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081947_93c62c32dc6d38ba7f06ff3a9596eb9a.png&h=03c7fd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081951_6148414a38ed89e02d0fe1f27c83eff3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081951_6148414a38ed89e02d0fe1f27c83eff3.png&h=dae4ef07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/081955_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F081955_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png&h=c366a968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60a56117e813fb5266a70d3c241852313eac900c","tid":1426022,"uid":2036,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:22:35.000Z","msg":"元朗滕條 鐵枝就睇唔到係攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"b0807216d1c4c13e036954ecc2ec2d41f6461ac1","tid":1426022,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:19.000Z","msg":"一個法西斯政府與其黨衛軍爪牙！"},{"pid":"cfa161384b522a73cc0e7cf7a5a337928253175c","tid":1426022,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，群眾鬥群眾，拉一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家要避免中林鄭圏套，林鄭就係想為示威者扣上港獨帽子，藉此分化和理非同前線關係，想重覆2014年雨革嗰一招！<br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，普羅大眾應該要明白呢一點，<span style=\"color: red;\">2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，和理非同埋勇武必須同心合作，互相掩護</span>，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f737b7671120b9159e4650bc472f4909002c07d","tid":1426022,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c76a96626479d02380e5a8064b963cd7385fb2e5","tid":1426022,"uid":2036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"希望記者會可以睇到<br />\n<br />\n今日有無記者會"},{"pid":"f684b1033d6ce9ceee225fe7973a3a04ecad6afa","tid":1426022,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76a96626479d02380e5a8064b963cd7385fb2e5","tid":1426022,"uid":2036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"希望記者會可以睇到<br />\n<br />\n今日有無記者會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:32:35.000Z","msg":"日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e447f0f9a26e1c542cb5bdad2c1f84fb739a73","tid":1426022,"uid":36238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"用啲閃光燈閃住阿sir做記者會啦"},{"pid":"2a14c1d321622c39fcdcddb350f355b2e854b72d","tid":1426022,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"重點係機場<br />\n<br />\n8月6日深水埗無差別拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da4e0aff52b2900408e2969de2cd936a01d9cf57","tid":1426022,"uid":7818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"最低程度武力=未撚打死你程度武力"},{"pid":"213995d96a04a2cecdf279c84b946e2f31259053","tid":1426022,"uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"er"},{"pid":"aadbcd658af28e9547a9179175c8a990c4bdaab0","tid":1426022,"uid":192136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"Er... 即係...er.... 之後.... 咁即係...."},{"pid":"36280a8a650811